              },
              "value": "3",
              "values": [
                {
                  "id": "1",
                  "label": {
                    "en": "1 phase",
                    "nl": "1 fase"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "3",
                  "label": {
                    "en": "3 phases",
                    "nl": "3 fasen"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "grid_fuse_A",
              "type": "number",
              "label": {
                "en": "Main fuse per phase (A)",
                "nl": "Hoofdzekering per fase (A)"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "Rated current of the main fuse per phase (e.g. 25 A for a 3×25 A connection). Load balancing will never allow the charger to exceed this value per phase.",
                "nl": "Nominale stroom van de hoofdzekering per fase (bijv. 25 A bij een 3×25 A aansluiting). Laadbalancering zorgt dat de lader deze waarde per fase nooit overschrijdt."
              },
              "value": 25,
              "units": {
                "en": "A",
                "nl": "A"
              },
              "attr": {
                "min": 10,
                "max": 63,
                "step": 1
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "max_current_limit",
              "type": "number",
              "label": {
                "en": "Charger cable max current (A)",
                "nl": "Laadkabel maximale stroom (A)"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "Rated maximum current of the charging cable or charger hardware (e.g. 16 A). Upper limit for the charge current slider and load balancing output.",
                "nl": "Maximale stroom van de laadkabel of hardware (bijv. 16 A). Bovengrens voor de laadstroom schuifregelaar en laadbalancering."
              },
              "value": 16,
              "units": {
                "en": "A",
                "nl": "A"
              },
              "attr": {
                "min": 6,
                "max": 32,
                "step": 1
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "meter_group",
          "type": "group",
          "label": {
            "en": "Energy meter (automatic load balancing)",
            "nl": "Energiemeter (automatische laadbalancering)"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "meter_device_id",
              "type": "text",
              "label": {
                "en": "Energy meter device ID",
                "nl": "Energiemeter device ID"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "Paste the Homey device ID of your energy meter here. Find it via Homey developer tools (https://developer.homey.app) or leave empty to use manual flow control. The device must expose measure_current.L1 (and L2, L3 for 3-phase).",
                "nl": "Plak hier het Homey device ID van uw energiemeter. Te vinden via de Homey developer tools (https://developer.homey.app) of leeg laten voor handmatige flowsturing. Het device moet measure_current.L1 (en L2, L3 bij 3-fase) beschikbaar stellen."
              },
              "value": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "lb_group",
          "type": "group",
          "label": {
            "en": "Load balancing",
            "nl": "Laadbalancering"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "id": "lb_enabled",
              "type": "checkbox",
              "label": {
                "en": "Enable load balancing keepalive",
                "nl": "Laadbalancering keepalive inschakelen"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "When enabled, Homey periodically rewrites the calculated max current to prevent fallback to safe current (Alfen validity time = 60 s).",
                "nl": "Indien ingeschakeld schrijft Homey het berekende max stroom periodiek opnieuw naar de lader om terugval naar de veilige stroom te voorkomen (Alfen geldigheidstijd = 60 s)."
              },
              "value": true
            },
            {
              "id": "lb_interval",
              "type": "number",
              "label": {
                "en": "Load balancing interval (s)",
                "nl": "Laadbalancering interval (s)"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "How often Homey rewrites the max current setpoint. Must be less than the Alfen validity time (default 60 s). Recommended: 30 s.",
                "nl": "Hoe vaak Homey het max stroom setpoint herschrijft. Moet kleiner zijn dan de Alfen geldigheidstijd (standaard 60 s). Aanbevolen: 30 s."
              },
              "value": 30,
              "units": {
                "en": "s",
                "nl": "s"
              },
              "attr": {
                "min": 10,
                "max": 59,
                "step": 1
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "lb_safety_margin_A",
              "type": "number",
              "label": {
                "en": "Safety margin per phase (A)",
                "nl": "Veiligheidsmarge per fase (A)"
              },
              "hint": {
                "en": "Subtracted from available current per phase before writing to the charger. Covers the measurement latency window between two P1 meter updates. DSMR 5.0 meters update every 1 s (use 1–2 A). DSMR 4.x meters update every 10 s or with high-impact loads (use 3–4 A). A higher margin reduces overload risk but also reduces maximum charge current.",
                "nl": "Wordt per fase van de beschikbare stroom afgetrokken voordat naar de lader wordt geschreven. Dekt het meetvertragingsvenster tussen twee P1-meterupdates. DSMR 5.0 meters geven elke 1 s een update (gebruik 1–2 A). DSMR 4.x meters geven elke 10 s een update of bij grote plotselinge lasten (gebruik 3–4 A). Een hogere marge verkleint het risico op overbelasting maar beperkt ook de maximale laadstroom."
              },
              "value": 1,
              "units": {
                "en": "A",
                "nl": "A"
              },
              "attr": {
                "min": 0,
                "max": 6,
                "step": 0.5
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
